@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tqpyih(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.45
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.abs((v2 + 0.51 / tmp + 0.64)))
    v1 = ((tmp * wp.abs(v2 + 0.97)) + ((v2 + 0.31 / v1 + 0.93) + (tmp + 0.50 + v0 + 0.11)))
    data[tid] = v0
